    <h1>Prominence (Local Ranking)</h1>
    <p class="description">One of Google's three core local ranking factors — and the only one you can actively build. Prominence measures how well-known your business is through <strong>reviews, citations, backlinks, and web presence</strong>.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
